Conky Bargraph made by Mario Zamora
Site: http://malbzamora.deviantart.com/

Instructions to install

1.- You need have installed Conky 1.8+
2.- Set the correct path on the conkyrc file for the "barras.lua" script
3.- Set the start.sh file to be loaded on the autostart of your system (this depends of your distro)
4.- You need have installed the two fonts added with this package

License: GPL3

Thanks to wlourf for the lua/cairo scripts

Enjoy and improve it!
